rComments: One of the worst profs I've ever encountered. He projected OneNote to the screen and typed out notes IN CLASS (please imagine the # of typos) and then read out his typed out words aloud to us! What a waste of time. He didn't add pictures or diagrams during these typing sessions, either. Just take a regular algo class and avoid ECE448 with him.

Lecture notes were messy and poorly organized. Contents were boring and overlapped with other bio and algorithm courses. No textbook. Tutorial was extremely useless. One of the worst courses ever taken.
He teaches Nothing. Even my friend who is the ECE top one gets confused. If you ask him a question. He always response you: YOU may be right.
This professor appears to not know anything other than what is on the slides, He reads them to you and make you fall asleep. constantly reads wrong too

Has completely trash lecture slides, and his lectures consist of reading them to you. Also makes quizzes on irrelevant topics that in no way test your knowledge of the subject. Thinks he's better than you and wants you to know it.
